<i>adjective</i>: 후끈후끈하다 [후끈후끈하다], 후끈하다 [후끈하다], 화끈화끈하다 [화끈화끈하다], 화끈하다 [화끈하다], 기름지다 [기름지다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>후끈후끈하다 [후끈후끈하다]</dt><br>
<dd>burning; glowing</dd><br>
<dd>뜨거운 느낌이 자꾸 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's face feeling hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dt>후끈하다 [후끈하다]</dt><br>
<dd>burning; glowing</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>An object feeling suddenly hot, being exposed to heat or one's face suddenly feeling hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dt>화끈화끈하다 [화끈화끈하다]</dt><br>
<dd>burning; glowing</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 느낌이 자꾸 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling suddenly hot in a repeated manner, being exposed to heat or one's face becoming suddenly hot and turning red in a repeated manner.</dd><br>
<dt>화끈하다 [화끈하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. burning; glowing</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling suddenly hot, being exposed to heat or one's face becoming suddenly hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unhesitating; without reserve; unhindered; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>일을 처리하는 방식이나 성격이 매우 시원스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's way of handling a task or personality being very unhesitating without reserve.</dd><br>
<dt>기름지다 [기름지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. greasy; oily</dd><br>
<dd>음식물이 기름기가 많다.</dd><br>
<dd>Greasy food.</dd><br>
<dd>2. greasy</dd><br>
<dd>사람이나 동물이 살이 많고 윤기가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>A person or animal being fat or looking greasy.</dd><br>
<dd>3. glowing</dd><br>
<dd>식물의 잎이나 줄기가 싱싱하고 윤기가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>A leaf or branch of a plant looking fresh and glossy.</dd><br>
<dd>4. fertile; rich</dd><br>
<dd>땅이 양분이 많다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a lot of nutrients in the land.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>